  "texts": [
    "We also specified that the summarization should be \"concise\" and use \"a minimal amount of text\" to avoid LLMs generating lengthy reports 13.",
    "Due to the size of candidate models, we opted for quantized low-rank adaptation (QLoRA) 37, a type of parameter efficient fine-tuning (PEFT) 38 to optimize our LLMs for echo report summarization tasks.",
    "The same prompt template was used, and the Final Impression text from the same report was used as the target output 13, 14.",
    "We configured the training process as follows: load model in 4-bit precision, with a LoRA configuration of (alpha = 16, LoRA dropout = 0.1, LoRA r= 64).",
    "The batch size and gradient accumulation were adjusted for each model to achieve an effective batch size of 24 that fits on a single NVIDIA RTX A5000 24G GPU setting."
  ],
